            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Completely disaster this branch is.. I got transferred in my bank job in chakan.\nI got my daughter admission in nursery..\nTeachers are extremely casual in approach about how she is studying.. every time when we meet them they mention all is good..  And for the whole year I saw no difference in her studies. Zero in all. Neither she knows a to z clearly not 1 to 10.\nI never understand what is she studying..coz teachers never bothered whether home work is completed or not.. never a phone call from them how is she doing gud or bad.\nOne day she came home with potty in her pants. No maid or teacher checked that she should be cleaned. They changed school timings in winter half an hour earlier despite of the fact many parents went to compliant that.. but of no use.this increased their absenteeism and later they blamed child is not doing well due to not being present.\nTeachers are unaware that timings are issue. Talk to principal or other senior teachers ..we don't take decision.\nInnumerous times I asked them to share pics videos of my daughter since this is my first year i want to relish those moments. How is she performing in festivals , different occassions etc.. teachers say We are not allowed to send pics talk to seniors. They simply refuse. Too much of professionalism.\n\nI didn't saw any gud change in my daughter with continuous complains , i don't have friends dere. No betterment in her. As if I am just sending in daycare. No efforts in curriculum..\n\nAll nd all, inexperienced staff.. Nd casual approach.",
